              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              If a street is more than one unit wide, it still only counts as a single crossing.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Constraints
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               map
              </b>
              will contain between 1 and 50 elements, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Each element of
              <b>
               map
              </b>
              will contain between 1 and 50 characters, inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Each element of map will contain only the characters '.', '-', '|', '*', 'F', 'S', 'H'.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              There will be exactly one occurrence each of 'S' and 'H' in
              <b>
               map
              </b>
              .
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
